         <abstract label="Abstract">This addition to the James J.
         Kilpatrick papers contains office files, 1950-1966, letters,
         speeches, articles, television debates, the Margaret Wagner
         file, and papers on Kilpatrick's books 
         <title render="italic">The Sovereign States</title>, 
         <title render="italic">The Smut Peddlers</title>, 
         <title render="italic">The Lasting South</title>, and 
         <title render="italic">The Southern Case</title>.</abstract>
      </did>
